snippet.title: holonoptic Trailer | nonlinear story game | business simulation | building management
snippet.description:
holonoptic is an upcoming nonlinear story game for PC, Linux and Mac.

www.glazial.com/holonoptic
We are testing potential applicants for the newly vacant position of CEO.

In holonoptic™, you will control our very own company, the Glazial Group, and face both psychological and economic challenges.

Our goal is to assess your ideological and mental compability with our company's new software, Geist_AI™.
